# 📚 Library Management System

A simple Library Management System built using **Python + SQL**.  
This project helps manage books, students, and borrowing/return records efficiently through a terminal-based interface.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Add, update, and delete book records  
- Add and manage student records  
- Issue and return books with due-date tracking  
- Search books by title, author, or ID  
- View all available and borrowed books  
- SQL database integration for data storage  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Python** (Core logic)  
- **MySQL** (Database management)  

---

## 📂 Project Structure
library_project/
│-- main.py # Entry point
│-- database.py # Database connection & queries
│-- book.py # Book management logic
│-- student.py # Student management logic
│-- requirements.txt # Dependencies (if any)
│-- README.md # Project documentation
